  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b93\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcb \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Auto fare increase",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Ceylon Auto Drivers' Association has announced that it will increase auto fares from today (26) following the increase in fuel prices.",
        "The association has announced that the auto fee will be increased by 10 rupees accordingly."
      ],
